{"title_page": "Minister of Justice and Public Security", "text_new": "In [[Norway]], the '''Minister of Justice and Public Security''' is the head of the [[Norwegian Ministry of Justice and the Police|Royal Norwegian Ministry of Justice and the Police]] and a member of [[Government of Norway]]. The current Justice Minister is [[Monica M\u00e6land]]. \n\nUntil 1 January 2012 the post was named the '''Minister of Justice and the Police'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.regjeringen.no/en/the-government/stoltenberg-ii.html?id=85843 |title=Members of the Government |publisher=Regjeringen.no |date=2009-06-19 |accessdate=2015-03-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.regjeringen.no/en/the-government/previous-governments/the-structure-of-the-registry/ministries-and-offices/government-secretariats-and-ministries-s/ministries-since-1814.html?id=426141 |title=Norwegian Government Ministries |publisher=Regjeringen.no |date=2014-03-31 |accessdate=2015-03-10}}</ref>\n\n==List of ministers==\n===2nd Ministry (justice affairs) (1814&ndash;1818)===\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n! scope=col class=unsortable | Photo\n! scope=col | Name\n! scope=col | Party\n! scope=col | Took office\n! scope=col | Left office\n! scope=col | Tenure\n! scope=col | Cabinet\n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Sommerhielm1_(cropped).jpg|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Mathias Sommerhielm]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 27 November 1814 || 15 June 1815 || {{age in years and days|1814|11|27|1815|6|15}} || Wedel I \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Christian_Adolph_Diriks_malt_av_Ragna_Hennig-Larsen_etter_silhuett_-_Eidsvoll_1814_-_EM.03071_-_crop.jpg|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Christian Adolph Diriks]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 15 June 1815|| 15 September 1816 || {{age in years and days|1815|6|14|1816|9|15}} || Wedel I \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Sommerhielm1_(cropped).jpg|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Mathias Sommerhie