mber 1814 || 15 June 1815 || {{age in years and days|1814|11|27|1815|6|15}} || Wedel I \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Christian_Adolph_Diriks_malt_av_Ragna_Hennig-Larsen_etter_silhuett_-_Eidsvoll_1814_-_EM.03071_-_crop.jpg|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Christian Adolph Diriks]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 15 June 1815|| 15 September 1816 || {{age in years and days|1815|6|14|1816|9|15}} || Wedel I \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Sommerhielm1_(cropped).jpg|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Mathias Sommerhielm]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 15 September 1816|| 15 May 1817 || {{age in years and days|1816|9|15|1817|5|15}} || Wedel I \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Christian_Adolph_Diriks_malt_av_Ragna_Hennig-Larsen_etter_silhuett_-_Eidsvoll_1814_-_EM.03071_-_crop.jpg|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Christian Adolph Diriks]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 15 May 1817|| 15 October 1817|| {{age in years and days|1817|5|15|1817|10|15}} || Wedel I \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Christian Krohg (politician).png|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Christian Krohg (government minister)|Christian Krogh]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 15 November 1817|| 4 March 1818|| {{age in years and days|1817|11|15|1818|3|4}} || Wedel I \n|-\n| align=center | [[File:Christian_Adolph_Diriks_malt_av_Ragna_Hennig-Larsen_etter_silhuett_-_Eidsvoll_1814_-_EM.03071_-_crop.jpg|75px]]\n! scope=row | [[Christian Adolph Diriks]]\n| style=\"background:#C0C0C0\" | [[Independent politician|Independent]] || 4 March 1818 || 1 January 1819|| {{age in years and days|1818|3|4|1819|1|1}} || Wedel I \n|-\n|}\n\n===Ministry of Justice and the Police (1819&ndash;1945)===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#efefef;\"\n! Name !! From !! To \n|-\n|[[Christian Adolph Diriks]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|1825\n|-\n|[[Poul Christia